The,EU,Open,Data,Portal,is,a,one,stop,shop,for,accessing,different,types,of,open,data,from,the,different,institutions,and,agencies,of,the,European,Union,Developers,seeking,to,deploy,EU,datasets,in,the,construction,of,third,party,applications,can,do,so,by,simply,using,the,EU,Open,Data,Portal,API,The,data,portal,can,be,accessed,through,either,the,RESTful,API,or,the,SPARQL,machine,readable,endpoint,This,API,sends,requests,and,returns,responses,in,JSON,format